items.title: Getting Started with Mobile Test Automation & Appium
items.description: Organizations today rely more and more on their mobile apps for their business. In fact, many companies now report that more than 50% of their traffic comes via a mobile device. In some cases, the mobile app may be the only way customers interact with a business or brand.
